Install:
   * Run "python setup.py bdist_egg"
   * Copy the created egg into the plugins folder of your project environment 

Requirements:
   * This plugin needs the "python-bibtex" package:
      Gentoo: "emerge python-bibtex"
      Debian: "apt-get install python-bibtex"
      Source: https://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=4825
